definition: can/may/able to/to approve/to permit/to suit/(particle used for emphasis) certainly/very

sentences.english: Jacobian matrix is one of the important parameters of robots.
sentences.chinese: 雅可比矩阵是描述机器人特征的重要参数之一。

sentences.english: The paper deals with the convegence of Riesz operators for Jacobi expansions.
sentences.chinese: 讨论了雅可比展开的黎斯算子的若干逼近性质。

sentences.english: Mr Dobson also has an unmatched power-base.
sentences.chinese: 杜布森还拥有无可比拟的权力基础。

sentences.english: Cabins can be up to seven square metres - that is bigger than many hotel rooms.
sentences.chinese: 包厢面积超过7平方米，这可比许多旅馆房间都要大。

sentences.english: There was more hoopla surrounding the introduction of incandescent lights than there seems to be surrounding compact fluorescents.
sentences.chinese: 当时，引进白炽灯可比引进紧凑荧光灯热闹许多。

sentences.english: The  grandeur of the  Old Summer Palace is second to none.
sentences.chinese: 圆明园的壮丽是其他园林无可比拟的。

sentences.english: BOD white water value in broken paper reclamation. It has unexampled excellent feature than anionic starch.
sentences.chinese: BOD的含量，具有阴离子型淀粉无可比拟的优点。

sentences.english: There is nothing to compare. And when we find incomparability, there is already half success," said Chen.
sentences.chinese: 找到了不可比性，就等于亚运会开幕式成功了一半。

sentences.english: I am Dr. kolb. How can I help you?
sentences.chinese: 我就是可比医生。我能帮你什么？

sentences.english: GDP growth rate is calculated at comparable prices.
sentences.chinese: 国内生产总值增长速度按可比价格计算。

sentences.english: This method doesn't compute the Moore-Penrose inverse of image Jacobian .
sentences.chinese: 这种方法无需计算雅可比矩阵伪逆。

sentences.english: The solutions of the formulas are very comparable with the solutions of 2-body problem.
sentences.chinese: 此组公式的解与二体问题解有很好的可比性。

sentences.english: But the plant moves more quickly than the  insect.
sentences.chinese: 但是这种植物的速度可比昆虫要快多了。

sentences.english: The proposed method simplifies Jacobian matrix of power system and saves calculation time.
sentences.chinese: 该方法简化了系统的雅可比矩阵，缩短了计算时间。

sentences.english: As for getting a feel for the life of locals, Wang Yuanyuan has more enthusiasm than me.
sentences.chinese: 要说感受市民的生活，王渊源的劲头儿可比我要大。

sentences.english: However, the two sets of numbers are not strictly comparable.
sentences.chinese: 然而，这两个数字严格来说并不具有可比性。
